@node "Introduction" "Introduction"
@next "Distribution"
@prev "Main"
This program made for people regulary work with Aminet index (f.e.downloading). There is some index manipulating programs (IndexMaker etc.),but on my 020+4Fast it work so slowly so i have not so patience to wait for ending of calculating.So i decide write my version of this kind of program. This my first program (something like 'Hello world' :-) ) so i hope you like my work .
@endnode

