@node "Features" "Features"
@prev "Author"
-GUI(at least!);

-filtering with optionaly enabled Age and NameMatching modes (via AND(&));

-fast(1MB=20secs on 68020+4Fast);

-percent displaying when processing;

-need no extra libraries (only gadtools 39+);

-calculating overall size of files and lines(files) of source(loaded index);

-automatic calculating size of files and quantity of files in processed index (before saving - it is useful);

-small size(less 40kB);
@endnode

@node "Usage" "Usage"
I try to make this program simlpy as possible,so i think there is no need to write a giant manual.You have just play with gadgets and you will understand all.There are just little hints:

-checkboxes disabled and enabled filtering modes.Default (right after start) name matching is disabled;

-modes filter via AND function (&)-only string that have right age and matches NamePattern will be copied into output buffer;

-"Analyze" button displays overall size of consisted files in index;

-after processing (filtering) if you dont save index and rechoose another procession mode,this dont saved index can not be restored (in other words original (loaded) index is always in main buffer);

-"FreeMem" simply frees memory (what's else?).
@endnode

@node "Technical Info" "Technical Info"
