@node "Bugs" "Bugs"
As i say it is my first program ever so program works on my machine very unstable.The biggest bug is crashing after closing program (in compiler/debug was OK! :-( ).So have patience and dont blame me if my program will crashed often.I have no possibilities to test IndexManager on other Amigas so please send me bugs reports.
@endnode

